    "body": "Yes I get the same results using chrome and chromium. They both return FFmpegVideoDecoder.\n\nAs far as I got hardware decoding has been disable on chromium because of instability (because of not so good graphic driver in linux).\n\nBut that would be fixed by now based on this issue, but i do not understand how:\nhttps://github.com/atom/libchromiumcontent/issues/92\n"
